</para>
<para id="element-19">The dimensionless γ is called Lorentz factor and dimensionless β is called speed factor. For small relative velocity, v, the terms <m:math>
  <m:mrow>
    <m:mrow>
      <m:msup>
        <m:mi>v</m:mi>
